key_trends: Increased adoption of AI-assisted software development

growth_bottlenecks: Building a comprehensive and reliable browser-native infrastructure
Educating the market on the benefits of this new approach

strengths: Addresses a critical gap in the AI-assisted software development lifecycle
concerns: Technology risk associated with browser limitations
Execution risk in building a comprehensive platform
